                  "id": "wc-act2-vane-success",
                  "act": 2,
                  "narrative": "Vane's resistance crumbles. He produces a torn page from an Order initiation manual \u2014 the Hermetic Primer \u2014 and lays it beside the cipher note. The symbols align perfectly. 'Someone has stolen our sacred script and turned it into a murder weapon,' he says, his voice tight with outrage. 'The cellar on Dorset Street \u2014 that is where the renegade chapter meets. I have been trying to expose them for months.' He gives you the address. His alibi, you note, is airtight.",
