                  "act": 2,
                  "narrative": "Mott's stained fingers freeze over the cipher note. His eyes widen \u2014 then narrow. 'Where did you get this?' he whispers. 'This typeface \u2014 I set it myself. Three months ago. A private commission, paid in gold sovereigns. The client wore gloves and spoke through a scarf.' He swallows hard. 'I kept a proof copy. I always keep proof copies.' He reaches beneath the counter and produces a sheet \u2014 the same symbols, but with a margin note in a different hand. An address in Bloomsbury.",
